{"thag7.4:0.1":"Theragatha 7.4 ","thag7.4:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thag7.4:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag7.4:0.4":"Sopakattheragatha ","thag7.4:1.1":"“Disva pasadachayayam, ","thag7.4:1.2":"cankamantam naruttamam; ","thag7.4:1.3":"Tattha nam upasankamma, ","thag7.4:1.4":"vandissam purisuttamam. ","thag7.4:2.1":"Ekamsam civaram katva, ","thag7.4:2.2":"samharitvana panayo; ","thag7.4:2.3":"Anucankamissam virajam, ","thag7.4:2.4":"sabbasattanamuttamam. ","thag7.4:3.1":"Tato panhe apucchi mam, ","thag7.4:3.2":"panhanam kovido vidu; ","thag7.4:3.3":"Acchambhi ca abhito ca, ","thag7.4:3.4":"byakasim satthuno aham. ","thag7.4:4.1":"Vissajjitesu panhesu, ","thag7.4:4.2":"anumodi tathagato; ","thag7.4:4.3":"Bhikkhusangham viloketva, ","thag7.4:4.4":"imamattham abhasatha. ","thag7.4:5.1":"‘Labha anganam magadhanam, ","thag7.4:5.2":"Yesayam paribhunjati; ","thag7.4:5.3":"Civaram pindapatanca, ","thag7.4:5.4":"Paccayam sayanasanam; ","thag7.4:5.5":"Paccutthananca samicim, ","thag7.4:5.6":"Tesam labhati cabravi. ","thag7.4:6.1":"Ajjatagge mam sopaka, ","thag7.4:6.2":"dassanayopasankama; ","thag7.4:6.3":"Esa ceva te sopaka, ","thag7.4:6.4":"bhavatu upasampada’. ","thag7.4:7.1":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","thag7.4:7.2":"laddhana upasampadam; ","thag7.4:7.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","thag7.4:7.4":"aho dhammasudhammata”ti. ","thag7.4:7.5":"… Sopako thero …. "}